<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ILIAS TIEDEMANN | Numerologische Analyse</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600&display=swap');

body {
  background: #050810;
  color: #F4E4A6;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 2rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.container {
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.2);
}

.header h1 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  color: #D4AF37;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.header .subtitle {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  color: #00d4ff;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.card {
  background: rgba(212,175,55,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.15);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #D4AF37, transparent);
}

.card h2 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  color: #D4AF37;
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.calc-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0.4rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.05);
}

.calc-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.calc-row .label {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: rgba(244,228,166,0.8);
}

.calc-row .value {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  color: #F4E4A6;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.calc-row .value.highlight {
  color: #D4AF37;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.calc-row .value.red { color: #ff6b6b; }
.calc-row .value.blue { color: #4ecdc4; }

.result-box {
  background: rgba(212,175,55,0.08);
  border: 2px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.3);
  border-radius: 15px;
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  margin: 2rem 0;
}

.result-box .signature {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: #D4AF37;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212,175,55,0.3);
}

.result-box .meaning {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: rgba(244,228,166,0.9);
  font-style: italic;
}

.comparison {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1rem;
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
}

.comp-card {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 1rem;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.1);
}

.comp-card .name {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  color: #D4AF37;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.comp-card .date {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  color: #00d4ff;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.comp-card .nums {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: #F4E4A6;
}

.comp-card .nums .sep {
  color: rgba(244,228,166,0.3);
  margin: 0 0.3rem;
}

.comp-card .nums .n { color: #ff6b6b; }
.comp-card .nums .d { color: #4ecdc4; }

.observation {
  background: rgba(255,107,107,0.05);
  border-left: 3px solid #ff6b6b;
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
  border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
}

.observation p {
  margin: 0.3rem 0;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: rgba(244,228,166,0.85);
}

.observation .alert {
  color: #ff6b6b;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 2rem;
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.1);
}

.footer .mantra {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: rgba(244,228,166,0.4);
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .comparison { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
<base target="_blank">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

<div class="header">
  <h1>ILIAS TIEDEMANN</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">Numerologische Analyse · 21.08.2004</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h2>1. Westliche Gematrie (A=1, B=2, ... Z=26)</h2>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">ILIAS: I(9) + L(12) + I(9) + A(1) + S(19)</span>
    <span class="value">= 50</span>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">TIEDEMANN: T(20) + I(9) + E(5) + D(4) + E(5) + M(13) + A(1) + N(14) + N(14)</span>
    <span class="value">= 85</span>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">Gesamtsumme</span>
    <span class="value highlight">50 + 85 = 135</span>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">Reduktion</span>
    <span class="value">135 → 1+3+5 = <span class="highlight">9</span></span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h2>2. Pythagoreische Numerologie (1-9)</h2>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">ILIAS: I(9) + L(3) + I(9) + A(1) + S(1)</span>
    <span class="value">= 23 → <span class="blue">5</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">TIEDEMANN: T(2) + I(9) + E(5) + D(4) + E(5) + M(4) + A(1) + N(5) + N(5)</span>
    <span class="value">= 40 → <span class="red">4</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">Gesamtsumme</span>
    <span class="value highlight">23 + 40 = 63</span>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">Reduktion</span>
    <span class="value">63 → 6+3 = <span class="highlight">9</span></span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h2>3. Datumsberechnung</h2>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">21.08.2004</span>
    <span class="value">2+1+0+8+2+0+0+4 = 17</span>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-row">
    <span class="label">Reduktion</span>
    <span class="value">17 → 1+7 = <span class="highlight">8</span></span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="result-box">
  <div class="signature">9 / 8</div>
  <div class="meaning">
    Name (9): Vollendung, Transformation, universelles Bewusstsein<br>
    Datum (8): Materie, Karma, Manifestation, Schicksal
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h2>4. Vergleich mit Chetan Nirup / Tim Bukowski</h2>
  <div class="comparison">
    <div class="comp-card">
      <div class="name">CHETAN NIRUP</div>
      <div class="date">20.11.1999</div>
      <div class="nums"><span class="n">3</span><span class="sep">/</span><span class="d">5</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="comp-card">
      <div class="name">TIM BUKOWSKI</div>
      <div class="date">21.08.1977</div>
      <div class="nums"><span class="n">9</span><span class="sep">/</span><span class="d">8</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="comp-card" style="border:2px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.4);">
      <div class="name">ILIAS TIEDEMANN</div>
      <div class="date">21.08.2004</div>
      <div class="nums"><span class="n">9</span><span class="sep">/</span><span class="d">8</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="observation">
  <p><span class="alert">⚠️ IDENTISCHE SIGNATUR:</span></p>
  <p>ILIAS TIEDEMANN teilt die exakte numerologische Signatur <strong>9/8</strong> mit TIM BUKOWSKI.</p>
  <p>Beide wurden am <strong>21.08.</strong> geboren – materielle Verankerung (8) am selben Tag.</p>
  <p>Beide tragen die Namenszahl <strong>9</strong> – Vollendung, Transformation, universelles Bewusstsein.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:0.8rem; color:#D4AF37;">Der Geist (Chetan/3/5) frequentiert Harmonie. Der Körper (Tim/9/8) manifestiert sie. ILIAS (9/8) manifestiert dieselbe Frequenz – 27 Jahre später, am selben Tag.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <div class="mantra">SEHE. ERKENNE. INTEGRIERE. ERWACHE. LEBE.</div>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
